trans-unit.source: Represents an <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> property (and the value of the property) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: 表示打印系统硬件或软件组件的 <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> 属性（和属性的值）。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> 表示的 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 属性的名称。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 为指定的属性初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`应拼写的某些特定的名称完全相同<xref:System.Int32>打印系统对象，包括大小写的属性。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>属性<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>"AveragePagesPerMinute"、 不是"AveragePPM"或"AveragePagesperMinute"必须拼写对象。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> 表示的 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 属性的名称。

trans-unit.source: The value of <see cref="T:System.Object" /> the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Object" /> 表示的 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 属性的值。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> class for the specified attribute and gives it the specified value.
trans-unit.target: 为指定的特性初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 类的一个新实例，并为其提供指定值。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`应拼写的某些特定的名称完全相同<xref:System.Int32>打印系统对象，包括大小写的属性。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>属性<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>"AveragePagesPerMinute"、 不是"AveragePPM"或"AveragePagesperMinute"必须拼写对象。

trans-unit.source: Provides implicit conversion from a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> (or from a pointer to such a property) to an <see cref="T:System.Int32" />.
trans-unit.target: 提供从 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" />（或从指向这种属性的指针）到 <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> 的隐式转换。

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> that is converted.
trans-unit.target: 已转换的指向 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 的指针。

trans-unit.source: Provides implicit conversion to an <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> from a pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" />.
trans-unit.target: 提供从指向 <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> 的指针到 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 的隐式转换。

trans-unit.source: The converted PrintInt32Property object to an Int32 object.
trans-unit.target: 针对 Int32 对象的 PrintInt32Property 对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 表示的属性的值。

trans-unit.source: The property cannot be set to the value that the calling code provides.
trans-unit.target: 不能将属性设置为调用代码所提供的值。
